data.description: Welcome home to Encino Estates. This country living neighborhood just north of the city of Dayton is a perfect getaway from the hustle of the city. This upgraded Jackson floor plan has great touches from the LVP flooring and cabinet lighting in the kitchen. Oversized living, dining and kitchen combination has amble space for entertaining. The large back porch allows for bird or deer gazing. Large slab foundation is ready for your building dreams, with electric and water already supplied. Low taxes and a 24 hour manned security guardhouse at the entrance.   Call your preferred agent today for your private showing.
